the scaffold has you create is an IN-SCOPE verification artifact, not a codebase change — a kickoff rule like "only write the lift file" does NOT forbid it, and you create then delete it as part of verifying. Navigate the iframe URL and verify every check against live getComputedStyle output before declaring the lift done.
