    <mapping class="structural" studio_source="arcade" studio_name="Modal" production_source="@devrev-web-internal/design-system-shared-raw-design-system/components/modal" production_name="Modal">
      <prop_delta from="open"/>
      <prop_delta from="onOpenChange"/>
      <slot_note>Studio's &lt;Modal.Root open onOpenChange&gt;…&lt;/Modal.Root&gt; collapses to production's top-level &lt;Modal open onOpenChange&gt;…&lt;/Modal&gt; — there is NO production Modal.Root. Move the open/onOpenChange props onto &lt;Modal&gt; itself and DROP the .Root wrapper.</slot_note>
      <slot_note>Inside, the subcomponents map 1:1: Modal.Content → Modal.Content, Modal.Header → Modal.Header (with Modal.Header.Title / .Actions / .Description), Modal.Body → Modal.Body, Modal.Footer → Modal.Footer. Modal.Close and Modal.Trigger also exist.</slot_note>
      <slot_note>Prior art (read before writing): libs/commerce/features/your-plan/src/components/switch-plan-confirm-dialog.tsx — &lt;Modal open onOpenChange size="480"&gt;&lt;Modal.Content&gt;&lt;Modal.Header&gt;&lt;Modal.Header.Title/&gt;&lt;/Modal.Header&gt;&lt;Modal.Body/&gt;&lt;Modal.Footer/&gt;&lt;/Modal.Content&gt;&lt;/Modal&gt;.</slot_note>
      <slot_note>Accessibility: production Modal.Content warns at runtime if there's no Modal.Header.Title (radix DialogTitle requirement). If the Studio source had no header title, add a Modal.Header.Title (visually-hidden if needed) rather than leaving the a11y advisory.</slot_note>
      <prior_art>
        <example path="libs/commerce/features/your-plan/src/components/switch-plan-confirm-dialog.tsx" covers="Modal (root) + Content + Header.Title + Body + Footer, no Modal.Root"/>
      </prior_art>
    </mapping>
  </frame_inventory>
  <scaffolding shape="ad-hoc">
    <description>These are the things a Studio frame never covers by itself. Engineer and agent divide between them.</description>
    <item status="required">Consider whether this fits an existing Tier-2/3 template (PageLayout, ListViewPage, SettingsPage)</item>
    <item status="required" path="libs/&lt;domain&gt;/shared/data-layer/src/use-&lt;entity&gt;.ts">Data-layer hook (useDL&lt;Entity&gt; query)</item>
    <item status="required" path="libs/&lt;domain&gt;/adapters/src/&lt;entity&gt;.ts">Adapter (API response → UI shape)</item>
    <item status="required" path="libs/&lt;domain&gt;/shared/data-layer/src/keys.ts">Query keys entry</item>
    <item status="required" path="STALE_TIMES_IN_MS.&lt;ENTITY&gt;">Stale time entry</item>
    <item status="required" path="apps/product/dr-router.tsx + libs/micro-apps/main/src/...">Route registration</item>
    <item status="required">Feature flag gate (useFeatureFlag)</item>
    <item status="required">Event tracker wiring (useEventTracker + track)</item>
  </scaffolding>
